ides.api.plugin.io
Class IOPluginManager

java.lang.Object
  ides.api.plugin.io.IOPluginManager

public class IOPluginManager
extends java.lang.Object

The manager of I/O plugins. Plugins which provide services for the saving/loading of DES models or related meta-data or for the import/export of different file formats must register with this manager in order to be available to the user.

Author:
christiansilvano, Lenko Grigorov
See Also:
FileIOPlugin, ImportExportPlugin

public FileIOPlugin getDataSaver(java.lang.Class<?> type)
Returns a plugin which is capable of saving DESModels of the given perspective (e.g. FSAModel). If no registered plugin is capable, returns null.

Returns:

registerDataLoader

                               java.lang.String type)

Parameters:
plugin - the plugin to be registered
type - the type of model which the plugin can load

registerMetaLoader

                               java.lang.String type,
                               java.lang.String tag)
Registers a plugin which can load meta-data with the given "tag" for the given type of DES models. The type of model and the "tag" are read from the IDES model files.
